
<span class='GTTabs_titles'><b>Translation</b></span><br />
Come, I&#8217;ll give you the flower<br />
Which grows only in me, which blooms only for you<br />
Come, I&#8217;ll give you the flower<br />
I&#8217;ll open for you all my tassels</p>
<p>I haven&#8217;t been dreaming of a spring, because I hold it in my hand<br />
I won&#8217;t announce eternity, I&#8217;m not afraid of death<br />
I will die to be born in you<br />
My dear</p>
<p>Come, I&#8217;ll give you the flower<br />
I was blooming for you, only you may pick me</p>
